Gitcoin,is,a,bitcoin,tipping,donation,platform,that,allows,people,from,around,the,web,to,donate,and,or,to,seek,funding,for,their,projects,applications,The,Gitcoin,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,this,feature,into,their,applications,Gitcoin,is,currently,built,based,on,the,Coinbase,API,therefore,developers,must,first,have,a,Coinbase,account,wallet,before,they,can,start,using,the,Gitcoin,API